iEmergence is a speculative fiction about the birth of artificial
iintelligence. It follows the scientists and business men
iresponsible for the project, and eventually the machine itself as
icomputation becomes thought and thought becomes intelligence. It
iasks questions about the nature of life, our place in the universe,
iand ultimately good vs evil.

